cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image recognition and classification. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as logos are often used in multimedia applications. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses copyright infringement detection and product recommendation, which are related to information retrieval. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) are also possible sub-categories as the proposed method involves training a neural network and the paper discusses contextual advertising, which may involve natural language processing.
